
:import chardet-falcon -all

Domain text RandomEncodings

Groupby _ text:
  | :label case
  | `detected = chardet.detect(case)`
  | 'encoding&language' encoding-lang? : both-right?
  | 'ballpark&language' ballpark-lang? : close?
  | 'encoding'          encoding?      : encoding-right?
  | 'ballpark'          close?         : encoding-close?
  | 'neither'           neither?       : has-neither?
  ;

Satisfy _ text:
  | both-right?
  | both-close?
  | encoding?
  | ballpark?
  | neither?
  ;
